---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Cookie Policy | Rank4AI" description="Cookie Policy for Rank4AI Ltd.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Cookies' }
    ]} />

    <h1 class="mb-2">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Effective date: 16 January 2026 | Last updated: 4 March 2026</p>
    <div class="prose max-w-none text-[15px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>This Cookie Policy explains how Rank4AI uses cookies and similar technologies on rank4ai.co.uk.</p>
      <h2>2. What Cookies Are</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website. They help websites function properly and provide insight into how the site is used.</p>
      <h2>3. How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to ensure the website functions correctly, understand how visitors use the site, and improve performance. We do not use cookies for advertising or cross-site tracking.</p>
      <h2>4. Types of Cookies</h2>
      <p><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Necessary for basic site functionality.</p>
      <p><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Collect aggregated information about how visitors use the site. Used for statistical analysis only.</p>
      <h2>5. Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p>You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect site functionality.</p>
      <h2>6. Contact</h2>
      <p>Email: info@rank4ai.co.uk<br>Website: <a href="/contact/">rank4ai.co.uk/contact</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
